<h4><a href="https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2020-10-13/doc-iiznezxr5736617.shtml">realme 发布 realme Q2 系列</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371417" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/3713b5f8591f1b6.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="493" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/3713b5f8591f1b6.jpg 600w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/3713b5f8591f1b6-360x296.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></p>
<p>昨天，realme 发布了 realme Q2 和 realme Q2 Pro 两款 5G 手机，搭载了天玑 800U 处理器和 120Hz 高刷屏。</p>
<p>realme Q2 采用了后置三摄组合，分别是 4800 万像素主摄、800 万像素 119° 超广角、微距镜头；搭载 5000mAh 大电池 + 30W 智慧闪充。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371418" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/686245a27d1c0de.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="494" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/686245a27d1c0de.jpg 600w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/686245a27d1c0de-360x296.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></p>
<p>realme Q2 Pro 采用了后置四摄组合，主摄为 4800 万像素，另外三颗镜头分别是 119° 超广角、人像镜头、微距镜头。续航方面，realme Q2 Pro 搭载了 4300mAh 电池 + 65W 智慧闪充。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/1039843.htm">小米发布真无线蓝牙耳机 Air 2 Pro</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371419" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/mi2.jpeg" alt="" width="1074" height="681" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/mi2.jpeg 1074w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/mi2-360x228.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/mi2-768x487.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/mi2-1024x649.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1074px) 100vw, 1074px" /></p>
<p>新浪消息，小米发布真无线主动降噪耳机 Air 2 Pro，定价 699 元。Air 2 Pro 提供 100-3000Hz 的宽频降噪效果，从低频到高频噪音都能够覆盖。</p>
<p>Air 2 Pro 采用了 LCP 液晶复合振膜与 12mm 的大尺寸动圈，声称可形成更醇厚悠远的声音。此外，小米还和网易云音乐 app 合作，用户可通过「鲸云音效」适配专为 Air 2 Pro 打造的模式。</p>
<h4><a href="https://weibo.com/2557129567/Jp0zCp05R?from=page_1006062557129567_profile&amp;wvr=6&amp;mod=weibotime">华为将举办 2020 年「5G 行业终端生态峰会」</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371420" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/002N3sdhly1gjnsejru6lj60u06cd1ky02.jpg" alt="" width="1067" height="524" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/002N3sdhly1gjnsejru6lj60u06cd1ky02.jpg 1067w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/002N3sdhly1gjnsejru6lj60u06cd1ky02-360x177.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/002N3sdhly1gjnsejru6lj60u06cd1ky02-768x377.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/002N3sdhly1gjnsejru6lj60u06cd1ky02-1024x503.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1067px) 100vw, 1067px" /></p>
<p>华为将于 10 月 16 日在北京举办 2020 年「5G 行业终端生态峰会」。届时，华为将发布《5G 行业终端生态白皮书》，宣布「5G 行业终端生态联盟」的建立。</p>
<h4>COLMO 太空舱洗衣机发布</h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371421" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/yinli.jpg" alt="" width="864" height="575" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/yinli.jpg 864w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/yinli-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/yinli-768x511.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 864px) 100vw, 864px" /></p>
<p>近日，美的集团发布 COLMO 太空舱洗衣机。官方声称，这款洗衣机了采用第四代冷萃银除菌技术，通过更加稳定的冷萃银晶体的长效缓释能力，达到更高效杀菌抑菌防护效果，杀菌率高达 99.9%。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293889" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://cn.technode.com/post/2020-10-13/china-internet-iudiovisual-development-report-2020/">我国网络视听用户规模破 9 亿，短视频人均使用时长已超过即时通讯</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371422" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/bd945eb7da9e4e8380ac33f1643e5cce.png" alt="" width="1598" height="988" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/bd945eb7da9e4e8380ac33f1643e5cce.png 1598w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/bd945eb7da9e4e8380ac33f1643e5cce-360x223.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/bd945eb7da9e4e8380ac33f1643e5cce-768x475.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/bd945eb7da9e4e8380ac33f1643e5cce-1024x633.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1598px) 100vw, 1598px" /></p>
<p>《2020 中国网络视听发展研究报告》显示，截至 2020 年 6 月，我国网络视听用户规模达 9.01 亿，网民使用率为 95.8% ，2019 年网络视听产业规模达 4541.3 亿。</p>
<p>在各个细分领域中，短视频的用户使用率最高，达 87.0%，用户规模 8.18 亿。短视频人日均使用时长于 2018 年下半年首次超过综合视频应用，而在今年 6 月，短视频更以人均单日 110 分钟的使用时长超越了即时通讯。</p>
<h4><a href="https://36kr.com/newsflashes/922695289833856">B 站国产动画活跃观众数量首次超过日本番剧</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371423" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/a8350c51fe594d51ac042a5a17ebbdae.jpeg" alt="" width="640" height="422" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/a8350c51fe594d51ac042a5a17ebbdae.jpeg 640w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/a8350c51fe594d51ac042a5a17ebbdae-360x237.jpeg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></p>
<p>36kr 消息，B 站 CEO 陈睿表示，2019 年，B 站国产动画活跃观众数量首次超过日本番剧，总播放时长破 3 亿小时。此外，今年 B 站单部收入最高的两部动画是国产动画《元龙》《仙王的日常生活》，超过了日本番剧。</p>
<p>三年内，B 站出品和投资了 93 部国产原创动画、90 部纪录片。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.zhitongcaijing.com/content/detail/346190.html">Netflix 停止在美国地区提供免费试用</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371424" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/7dcc-hzxsvnp4950719.jpg" alt="" width="1400" height="700" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/7dcc-hzxsvnp4950719.jpg 1400w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/7dcc-hzxsvnp4950719-360x180.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/7dcc-hzxsvnp4950719-768x384.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/7dcc-hzxsvnp4950719-1024x512.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px" /></p>
<p>智通财经消息，Netflix 停止在美国地区提供流媒体免费试用制度。官方发言人表示，公司正在美国寻求不同的市场推广方式来吸引新会员。</p>
<p>据悉，本月开始，Netflix 将逐步取消免费试用制度，但将设置一个促销窗口，让观众可免费观看部分热门剧。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.jiemian.com/article/5106235.html">青岛警方：发布夸大确诊人数虚假信息网友被行拘 15 日</a></h4>
<p>青岛市公安局市北分局通报，10 月 12 日晚，多名网友向青岛警方举报，网友井某某在新浪微博发布夸大青岛新冠肺炎确诊人数的虚假信息。</p>
<p>经公安审查，井某某对其为吸引微博人气，编造青岛市新冠肺炎确诊人数的虚假信息在新浪微博予以发布的违法事实供认不讳。现井某某已被依法行政拘留 15 日并处罚金 500 元。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357461" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife.png" alt="" width="1029" height="153" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-360x54.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-768x114.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-1024x152.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://static.nfapp.southcn.com/content/202010/13/c4148129.html">广州 22 号线或成第一条连接广深的地铁线路</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371425" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/16_9.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="720" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/16_9.jpg 1280w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/16_9-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/16_9-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/16_9-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /></p>
<p>《广州日报》消息，相关招标书显示，广州除了已公布的 18 号线南延至中山珠海、28 号线东延至东莞之外，22 号线也规划成为跨市快线，将延伸至东莞，与深圳衔接，有望成为第一条连接广深的地铁线路。</p>
<p>相关规划设计人士透露，最早规划时的 22 号线主要服务于广州南站与南沙的高速联络。如今 22 号线「升级」成为大湾区城际，如果可通过优化设计，确保快车只停重要站点，将进一步缩短广深莞的时空距离，提升都市圈高速轨道的效益。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CCY2G7Tn3Ig/">《头号玩家》续集小说将于 11 月出版</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371426" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/106734087_293008642060210_1210289040377653120_n.jpg" alt="" width="1080" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/106734087_293008642060210_1210289040377653120_n.jpg 1080w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/106734087_293008642060210_1210289040377653120_n-360x360.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/106734087_293008642060210_1210289040377653120_n-768x768.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/106734087_293008642060210_1210289040377653120_n-1024x1024.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px" /></p>
<p>《头号玩家》官方 Instagram 宣布，电影原着小说续集《Ready Player Two》将于今年 11 月 24 日正式出版，现在已经开始接受预订。</p>
<p>早在 2018 年，电影女主角 Olivia Cooke <a href="https://popbee.com/lifestyle/movies/ready-player-one-star-signed-on-sequels/">已经对外宣布</a>自己和电影公司签订了电影续集的合约。随着小说续集的到来，电影续集也越来越近了。</p>
<h4><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/SZ7_NkSqQYOIFG9C-6nq-Q">从代言人到股东，谢霆锋入股特步</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371427" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/641b-ietnfsp4386490.jpg" alt="" width="2048" height="1406" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/641b-ietnfsp4386490.jpg 2048w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/641b-ietnfsp4386490-360x247.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/641b-ietnfsp4386490-768x527.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/641b-ietnfsp4386490-1024x703.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px" /></p>
<p>《中国经营报》消息，近日，特步披露，其形象代言人谢霆锋同意认购特步国际 500 万股股份，每股认购价为 2.48 港元，总价格为 1240 万港元，折合人民币约 1070 万元。</p>
<p>此次特步国际向谢霆锋发行 500 万股，占已扩大发行股本约 0.2%。根据协议，谢霆锋一年内不会卖股。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293890" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E5%BD%93%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%BE%88%E4%B9%85%E6%B2%A1%E6%8D%A2%E8%BF%87%E5%A4%B4%E5%83%8F%23&amp;Refer=top">当一个人很久没换过头像</a></h4>
<p>当一个人很久没换过头像，大家会不会下意识认为他就长头像那样？</p>
<p>网友：「真的，对于不太熟的人，换了个头像就感觉就不认识了。」「何止头像，如果一个人常用特定表情包，还慢慢觉得他越来越像那个表情包呢。」</p>
➜逛完这条「灵感隧道」，我的 Apple Watch 心率差点爆表！
https://www.ifanr.com/1371527?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=	19763
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1371549" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/3.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="720" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/3.jpg 1280w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/3-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/3-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /></p>
<p>小伙伴们都懂的，有趣的人儿，总压不住压马路的冲动。</p>
<p>谁还不是个不安分的宝宝呢？</p>
<p>前阵子路过广州未来社这个网红打卡点，有个瞬间，是被击中的感觉。</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>我也常自觉创意无极限，脑洞大过天。</p>
<p>一说到创意，往往意味着突破常规，甚至令人猝不及防，比如……你以为我要举个例子。</p>
<p>而我只是看到了一条隧道。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1371528" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/84.png" alt="" width="1125" height="752" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/84.png 1125w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/84-360x241.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/84-768x513.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/84-1024x684.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1125px) 100vw, 1125px" /></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1371529" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/85.png" alt="" width="1080" height="1617" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/85.png 1080w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/85-360x539.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/85-768x1150.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/85-684x1024.png 684w" sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px" /></p>
<p>这啥？……「灵感隧道」？</p>
<p>“灵感是一种实物，它穿行在一条霓虹隧道，呈现着多维度的纷呈可能”，</p>
<p>大胆的颜色，骚柔的文字，还有散落人间的小姐姐……</p>
<p>当逛不逛，必受其乱，话不多说，走起！</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1371530" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/86.png" alt="" width="1125" height="751" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/86.png 1125w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/86-360x240.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/86-768x513.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/86-1024x684.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1125px) 100vw, 1125px" /></p>
<p>年轻人都是颜值控，进隧道的瞬间我更不舍得老去了。</p>
<p>满眼都是年轻、颜值、酷炫。</p>
<p>爷青回！</p>
<p>颜色仿佛光线，差点音乐就能蹦迪。</p>
<p>置身其中，会有种恍惚，</p>
<p>不确定是跳跃的色彩迷了我的眼，</p>
<p>或是骚动的灵感入了我的魂。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1371531" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/87.png" alt="" width="1125" height="752" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/87.png 1125w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/87-360x241.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/87-768x513.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/87-1024x684.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1125px) 100vw, 1125px" /></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1371532" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/88.png" alt="" width="1080" height="1617" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/88.png 1080w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/88-360x539.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/88-768x1150.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/88-684x1024.png 684w" sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px" /></p>
<p>走过「灵感隧道」，就像在无限的创意中穿行，</p>
<p>让人不自觉有种逛 “脑回路” 的感觉，</p>
<p>比吃烤脑花还兴奋。</p>
<p>细心的 Apple Watch 已经发现，</p>
<p>我的心率与创意齐飞，秋水共长天一色。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1371533" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/89.png" alt="" width="1125" height="752" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/89.png 1125w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/89-360x241.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/89-768x513.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/89-1024x684.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1125px) 100vw, 1125px" /></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1371534" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/90.png" alt="" width="1125" height="752" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/90.png 1125w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/90-360x241.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/90-768x513.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/90-1024x684.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1125px) 100vw, 1125px" /></p>
<p>出来「灵感隧道」，现场也是一片青春洋溢，活脱脱一个网红打卡点，</p>
<p>扒拉工作人员一问，才知道是「广汽传祺全国大学生广告创意挑战赛」开幕仪式。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1371535" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/91.png" alt="" width="1125" height="751" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/91.png 1125w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/91-360x240.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/91-768x513.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/91-1024x684.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1125px) 100vw, 1125px" /></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1371536" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/92.png" alt="" width="1080" height="1617" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/92.png 1080w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/92-360x539.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/92-768x1150.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/92-684x1024.png 684w" sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px" /></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1371537" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/93.png" alt="" width="1125" height="751" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/93.png 1125w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/93-360x240.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/93-768x513.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/93-1024x684.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1125px) 100vw, 1125px" /></p>
<p>开幕式签到区布置得相当到位，大胆撞色的主视觉，加上各种逗趣的 “金句板”，不时出没的小姐姐小哥哥们，很明显，年轻是一个「人传人」的症状。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1371538" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/94.png" alt="" width="1125" height="752" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/94.png 1125w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/94-360x241.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/94-768x513.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/94-1024x684.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1125px) 100vw, 1125px" /></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1371539" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/95.png" alt="" width="1125" height="752" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/95.png 1125w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/95-360x241.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/95-768x513.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/95-1024x684.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1125px) 100vw, 1125px" /></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1371540" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/96.png" alt="" width="1125" height="752" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/96.png 1125w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/96-360x241.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/96-768x513.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/96-1024x684.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1125px) 100vw, 1125px" /></p>
<p>开场嘉宾请的是广州 Underground Band「小笼包乐队」。</p>
<p>“每个成员代表每个包子，包馅即是每个包子的想法”，</p>
<p>看完包子表演感觉很过瘾，但是听饿了。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1371541" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/97.png" alt="" width="1125" height="752" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/97.png 1125w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/97-360x241.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/97-768x513.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/97-1024x684.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1125px) 100vw, 1125px" /></p>
<p>还好不止有包子！</p>
<p>酒会、日料、西式餐点，</p>
<p>现场的晚宴不仅是吃货们的狂欢，</p>
<p>更是潮流、多元文化的交流、碰撞与融合。</p>
<p>真香！</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1371542" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/98.png" alt="" width="1125" height="752" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/98.png 1125w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/98-360x241.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/98-768x513.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/98-1024x684.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1125px) 100vw, 1125px" /></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1371543" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/99.png" alt="" width="1125" height="752" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/99.png 1125w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/99-360x241.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/99-768x513.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/99-1024x684.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1125px) 100vw, 1125px" /></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1371544" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/100.png" alt="" width="1125" height="752" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/100.png 1125w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/100-360x241.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/100-768x513.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/100-1024x684.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1125px) 100vw, 1125px" /></p>
<p>作为活动的重头戏，开幕仪式上也是星光熠熠，大咖齐聚。</p>
<p>创意大咖组成的 “导师天团”，也带我们逛了一圈「灵感隧道」</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1371545" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/101.png" alt="" width="1125" height="752" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/101.png 1125w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/101-360x241.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/101-768x513.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/101-1024x684.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1125px) 100vw, 1125px" /></p>
<p><iframe src="https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=x3160jtz1vq" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></p>
<p>据了解，这个赛事面向全国大学生征集创意广告作品，有趣的活动和诱人的奖品多多！</p>
<ul>
<li>“巨型创意盲盒” 开学礼派发活动</li>
<li>“不公开课” 校园宣讲</li>
<li>“才华市集” 创意比赛</li>
<li>广汽传祺、爱范儿、优必选、省广、王老吉、奈雪的茶等 50 份名企实习机会</li>
<li>创意热店启动资金</li>
<li>全国头部媒体曝光机会</li>
</ul>
<p>整场活动逛下来，有这么一种感觉：为了大大地引起脑洞大大的大学生们的注意，主办方简直煞费苦心，这是现场的招募视频，你们稍微感受一下。</p>
<p><iframe src="https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=e3159lnpe74" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></p>
<p>活动结束后找现场小姐姐撩到了一些报名的信息，有兴趣的同学可以了解一下。</p>
<p>这次大赛是由广汽传祺主办，面向全国各类高等院校在校全日制大学生、研究生的全国性创意大赛，意在挖掘校园创意，激发大学生创意思维，加强大学生实践能力、创新能力和合作能力，选拔优秀创意人才。</p>
<p>活动官网：<a href="#/"><u>https://gac-creative.ifanrusercontent.com/#/</u></a></p>
<p>另外还有个小小福利，现在去广州未来社打卡「灵感隧道」，可以去脱壳咖啡前台兑换指定咖啡哦！</p>
<p>嗯，这波羊毛值得一薅。</p>
