➜iPhone 12 选购指南：30 秒标签法「秒选」mini、12 、Pro 和 Max
https://www.ifanr.com/1371442?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=	19947
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">受疫情影响，今年新一代 iPhone 迟了一个月左右才和我们见面，「四大天王」—— <strong>mini、12、Pro 和 Pro Max 共同登场</strong>，堪称苹果发布会的史无前例。</span></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371450" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone121.png" alt="" width="1312" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone121.png 1312w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone121-360x227.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone121-768x485.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone121-1024x646.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1312px) 100vw, 1312px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 从左到右依次为：iPhone 12 Pro Max、iPhone 12 Pro、iPhone 12 和 iPhone 12 mini</p>
</div>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">四款全新 iPhone 既在某些硬件和功能上相同或相似，又在不少维度有着天壤之别，相信让很多「持币观望」的朋友犹豫不决。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">每年到新品发售季，下单时间慢几分钟，都有可能导致收货时间多几星期，为了帮助大家迅速决策购买哪款 iPhone，<strong>我们连夜制作了这份 iPhone 12 选购指南，希望能帮助你选择适合你的 iPhone 12</strong>。</span></p>
<h3 class="ql-long-24360693" data-header="1"><strong><span class="ql-author-24360693">30 秒回顾苹果发布会</span></strong></h3>
<p><center><iframe src="https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=z3160m348wf" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></center></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">相信大家能一眼看出 iPhone 12 系列的最大变化，那就是外观设计。四款机型都采取了类似 iPhone 4 的直角设计语言，弧度和曲线被更加硬朗的元素取代，颇有点致敬乔布斯时代的意思。</span></p>
<h3 class="ql-long-24360693" data-header="1"><strong><span class="ql-author-24360693">「四大天王」异同点</span></strong></h3>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">苹果一共发布了四款 iPhone 12，分别是 iPhone 12 mini、iPhone 12、iPhone 12 Pro 和 iPhone 12 Pro Max。</span></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371455" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone122.png" alt="" width="2078" height="1060" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone122.png 2078w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone122-360x184.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone122-768x392.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone122-1024x522.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2078px) 100vw, 2078px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 从左到右依次为：iPhone 12 Pro、iPhone 12、iPhone 12 mini</p>
</div>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><strong>首先我们来看看它们的主要共同点：</strong></p>
<ul>
<li class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">都支持 5G，都有 4G 和 5G 智能调度省电功能</span></li>
<li class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">屏幕都是 XDR Display，屏幕</span></span><span class="ql-author-24360693">最大 HDR 亮度都是 1200 尼特</span></li>
<li><span class="ql-author-24360693">都使用了超瓷晶面板，抗摔提升 4 倍</span></li>
<li>都缩减了边框宽度</li>
<li class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">都搭载 5nm A14 仿生芯片</span></li>
<li class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">都可以拍摄杜比视界 HDR 视频</span></li>
<li class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">都支持智能 HDR 3、Deep Fusion（深度融合）和夜景模式</span></li>
<li>超广角摄像头都支持夜景模式</li>
<li>都达到了 IP68 级防水标准</li>
<li><strong>都支持中国北斗</strong></li>
<li class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">都支持 20w 有线快充，15w 无线快充</span></li>
<li>都兼容 MagSafe 磁吸配件和无线充电器</li>
<li class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">都不再附送耳机和充电头</span></li>
</ul>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">值得注意的是，目前国际上 5G 有 Sub-6 和毫米波两个频段，现在中国大陆地区建设的 5G 为 Sub-6，而<strong>四款 iPhone 12 机型暂时也只支持 Sub-6，不支持毫米波</strong>（有可能是通过软件限制实现的）。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">所以<strong>手持 iPhone 12 在大陆地区使用是没有影响的</strong>，</span><span class="ql-author-24360693">即使到其它国家或地区，也可以使用 5G 的 Sub-6，大陆版本的 iPhone 12 是否能在别的国家或地区使用 5G 毫米波，可以关注我们后续的相关文章。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><strong><span class="ql-author-24360693">再来看它们的主要不同点：</span></strong></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371524" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone1232.png" alt="" width="1348" height="1056" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone1232.png 1348w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone1232-360x282.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone1232-768x602.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone1232-1024x802.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1348px) 100vw, 1348px" /></p>
<div data-header="1">
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 红色部分是需要格外注意的地方</p>
</div>
</div>
<h3 data-header="1"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371358" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/tUbRvGEzR73ioPiq__original.png" alt="" width="1536" height="864" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/tUbRvGEzR73ioPiq__original.png 1536w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/tUbRvGEzR73ioPiq__original-360x203.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/tUbRvGEzR73ioPiq__original-768x432.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/tUbRvGEzR73ioPiq__original-1024x576.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px" /></h3>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 特别提示，iPhone 12 mini 为单卡手机</p>
</div>
<h3 class="ql-long-24360693" data-header="1"><strong><span class="ql-author-24360693">更科学的选购逻辑是怎么样的？</span></strong></h3>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">我们设计了两个「购买金字塔」，帮助大家理顺决策逻辑。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><strong><span class="ql-author-24360693">第一种是需求驱动型，从实用性出发开始决策。</span></strong></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">明确自身需求 → 选择能满足需求的 iPhone 机型 → 确认该机型价格可以承担 → 选择合适的颜色→购买</span></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371554" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iphone1241.jpg" alt="" width="2065" height="1035" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iphone1241.jpg 2065w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iphone1241-360x180.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iphone1241-768x385.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iphone1241-1024x513.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2065px) 100vw, 2065px" /></p>
<p><strong><span class="ql-author-24360693">第二种是审美驱动型，从外观出发开始决策。</span></strong></p>
<p><span class="ql-author-24360693">选择喜欢的颜色 → 确认该机型价格可以承担 → 明确自身需求 → 选择能满足需求的 iPhone 机型 → 购买</span></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371555" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone1240.jpg" alt="" width="2131" height="985" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone1240.jpg 2131w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone1240-360x166.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone1240-768x355.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone1240-1024x473.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2131px) 100vw, 2131px" /></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">当然，以上只是两种大致区分方式，还是要看每个人的实际情况，大家可以按需选择。 </span></p>
<h3 class="ql-long-24360693" data-header="1"><strong><span class="ql-author-24360693">标签选购法，30 秒确定买哪款</span></strong></h3>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371456" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/cdf.jpg" alt="" width="3244" height="1814" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/cdf.jpg 3244w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/cdf-360x201.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/cdf-768x429.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/cdf-1024x573.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3244px) 100vw, 3244px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 以上四部手机均为 iPhone 12 Pro 系列</p>
</div>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">我们给四款 iPhone 12 分别打上了一些标签，标注出了它们最明显的特征，大家可以按照自己的决策流程，选取相应的一些关键词，组合到一起，选购合适的 iPhone 12。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693"> 下图中，<strong>红色标签代表独一无二的产品特征，蓝色标签代表较为重要的稀缺产品特征</strong>。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371494" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone129.png" alt="" width="1134" height="534" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone129.png 1134w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone129-360x170.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone129-768x362.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone129-1024x482.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1134px) 100vw, 1134px" /></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">假设我是一个需求驱动型用户，我的需求是<strong>大屏影音效果、最长的续航、五倍变焦</strong>，很显然只有 iPhone 12 Pro Max 满足我的需求，再结合决策逻辑来看，我愿意花大约 9000 元解决我的需求，价格这一关过了，最后四个颜色中有我喜欢或者可以接受的，就可以下单了。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">如果我是一个审美驱动型用户，我喜欢今年新出的淡绿色机型，又想用 6 寸屏幕以上的手机，而且觉得 64G 就够用了，关键词选择分别就是<strong>多彩、 6.1 英寸、64G</strong>，符合我审美，又满足价格和需求的，显然是 iPhone 12。</span></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371355" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/5-2.png" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/5-2.png 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/5-2-360x203.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/5-2-768x432.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/5-2-1024x576.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 由于边框宽度的缩小， 6.7 英寸 iPhone 12 Pro Max 只比 6.5 英寸 iPhone 11 Pro Max 大「一丢丢」</p>
</div>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">当然，也会有不少人会说「我全都要」，那我们建议把选取的标签全部列出来，看看哪款机型的标签和选出来的标签重叠度最高。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">有了金字塔图片和标签表格，是不是觉得决策过程轻松一些了呢？</span></p>
<h3 class="ql-long-24360693" data-header="1"><strong><span class="ql-author-24360693">哪些渠道可以订购？</span></strong></h3>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">和往年一样，四款 iPhone 12 都可以在苹果官网、线下 Apple Store、苹果授权店、第三方网购平台等途径预购或预订。</span></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371496" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone1210.png" alt="" width="1232" height="448" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone1210.png 1232w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone1210-360x131.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone1210-768x279.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/iPhone1210-1024x372.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1232px) 100vw, 1232px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 第三方网购平台仅统计官方渠道的信息，需要注意的是拼多多 iPhone 12 预约入口里提供服务的都是网店商家</p>
</div>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">如果是线下，我们更推荐大家通过苹果官方线下 Apple Store 店购买，购买之前最好打电话询问是否有现货。</span><span class="ql-author-24360693">如果是线上，我们更推荐大家通过苹果官网购买，备货量和派送效率方面相对更有保障。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">另外，不同国家和地区的 iPhone 12 折合成人民币有一定的价格优势，例如港版 iPhone 12 Pro 128GB 售价为 8499 港币，折合人民币约 7400 元，相当于打了 89 折，<strong>鉴于目前疫情状况，建议大家谨慎考虑</strong>。</span></p>
<h3 class="ql-long-24360693" data-header="1"><strong><span class="ql-author-24360693">从 iPhone 12 看苹果的策略改变</span></strong></h3>
<div data-header="1"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371451" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/price.jpg" alt="" width="3226" height="1810" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/price.jpg 3226w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/price-360x202.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/price-768x431.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/price-1024x575.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3226px) 100vw, 3226px" /></div>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">从「一部手机打天下」，到如今「四大天王齐登场」，反映的是苹果的产品策略调整。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">从价格区间来看，<strong>iPhone 一次性铺满从 3299（SE）&#8211; 11899（12 Pro Max）元的价格区间</strong>，覆盖了很多用户的购机预算范围。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">从 iPhone 12 机型来看，既有可以方便单手握持的 iPhone 12 mini，也有兼顾屏幕尺寸和性价比的 iPhone 12，还有为 Pro 级用户提供的旗舰入门级 iPhone 12 Pro，更有为追求极致用户打造的 iPhone 12 Pro Max。</span></p>
<p class="ql-long-24360693"><span class="ql-author-24360693">配合以前代 iPhone 守住更低价位区间，<strong>iPhone 可以说在这一代正式完成了「果式机海」战略布局，意味着其它手机厂商面临的竞争压力将更大</strong>，再加上用户的换机频率越来越低，用户对单一系统的生态依赖性也很难被改变，可以预测，未来的手机市场竞争会更加激烈。</span></p>
<div id="ifanr_profile" style="border:1px solid #ccc;font-size:14px;margin:27px auto;font-family:Arial;">
<div style="overflow:hidden"><a target="_blank" href="https://www.ifanr.com/author/zhuhai" style="color:#000;text-decoration:none;"></a>
<div style="text-align:left;line-height:23px;margin-left:80px">
<div style="padding:10px 10px 10px 0">
<div style="margin:0;font-size: 14px;"><strong><a target="_blank" href="https://www.ifanr.com/author/zhuhai" style="color:#000;text-decoration:none;">朱 海</a></strong>
</div>
<div style="font-size: 13px; line-height:20px;">三流方案策划者，二流出镜主持人，一流败家浪荡侠</div>
